title: Erick Figueroa Ildefonso
text: I’m a Peruvian researcher interested in the study of genetic adaptation and co-evolution of humans and non-human primates and their parasites like those from the genus Plasmodium. I’m specially interested in conducting studies in evolutionary genetics in populations with history of admixture.
